<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Attribute> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Attribut"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Attribute> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Attribute"@en .
