<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A change type is a category of changes defined by common characteristics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un type de changement est une catégorie de changements définie par des caractéristiques communes."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Change Type"@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#ChangeType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Type de changement"@fr .
