# https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Event describing a development involving one or more resources at a given time."@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un événément décrit une évolution impliquant une ou plusieurs ressources à un instant donné."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Event> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Event"@en .
