# 
# https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#Landmark
# 
# https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Il s'agit d'une relation qui représente un lien existant entre un ou plusieurs repères.\r\n    Ces relations peuvent prendre diverses formes, notamment :\r\n    - des relations géographiques, par exemple lorsqu'un point de repère est situé à l'angle de deux autres points de repère ;\r\n    - des relations hiérarchiques, par exemple lorsqu'un point de repère est la capitale d'une autre entité administrative ;\r\n    - d'autres relations spécifiques."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "It is a relation that represents a relation existing between one or more landmarks.\r\n    Such relations may take various forms, including:\r\n    - geographic relations, for example when a landmark is located at the corner of two other landmarks;\r\n    - hierarchical relations, for example when a landmark is the capital of another administrative entity;\r\n    - as well as other domain-specific or contextual relations depending on the application needs.\r\n    "@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Landmark relation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkRelation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Relation entre repères"@fr .
# 
# https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A type of landmark is a category that allows classifying the different types of landmarks."@en .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un type de repère est une catégorie qui permet de classer les différents types de repères."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#> .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Type de repère"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/PeGazUs#LandmarkType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Type of landmark"@en .
